tion effects, different types of initial conditions and hydrodynamical\nschemes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Jan 2017 09:09:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Mar 2017 18:42:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-22"}
