 the reach of the LHC and future\ncolliders.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Jan 2017 09:32:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 May 2017 09:16:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-10"}
